<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10094386>
    dc:description "PLATE 2. Figures 1–8. Tactusa species, adults. 1, 2, T. nilssoni, male holotype, Thailand, Phuket, and female paratype, with same data; 3, T. ostium, female holotype, Thailand, Nakhon Naoyk; 4, T. peregovitsi, male holotype, Vietnam N, Nghe Aniwan; 5, T. flavoniger, female holotype, Laos, Vientiane; 6, T. nieukerkeni, male holotype, Vietnam, Vinh Phuc; 7, T. topi, male holotype, China, Guangdong, Canton; 8, T. incognita, male holotype, Thailand, Nakhon Naoyk." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10094386/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

